NextJS Guidelines :

- Never use window.location.href, always `useRouter`

Component Structure:

- Over 3 sub-components? Create new file
- No inline callbacks, create functions instead
- Extract all top-level variables from component
- Variables only for rendering, view, UI, URLs

```typescript
function CourseCard({ course }: Props) {
  const handleClick = () => router.push(`/courses/${course.id}`);
  
  return (
    <Card onClick={handleClick}>
      <Text>{course.title}</Text>
    </Card>
  );
}
```
